devdoc.details: Contract is responsible for fees calculations.

calculateDepositBridgeFee(uint256).details: Calculate and return fee for deposit through bridge.

calculateDepositFee(uint256).details: Calculate and return deposit fee amount based on massetAmount.

calculateRedeemBridgeFee(uint256).details: Calculate and return fee for redeem through bridge.

calculateRedeemFee(uint256).details: Calculate and return redeem fee amount based on massetAmount.

params._depositBridgeFee: Amount of deposit through bridge fee in promils.
params._depositFee: Amount of deposit fee in promils.
params._withdrawalBridgeFee: Amount of redeem through bridge fee in promils.
params._withdrawalFee: Amount of redeem fee in promils.

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
